    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i see. so if i'm looking at a client who is black, would it be more efficient to lean into that high-intensity/explosive stuff right away based on what you're saying? and for a white client, should i prioritize building their aerobic base first to account for those slow-twitch fibers? just trying to understand if it's better to work with these natural predispositions rather than fighting against them.",
